summary: Doctor Who? What? Why? (A Short Rant In Time And Space)
title: Doctor Who? What? Why? (A Short Rant In Time And Space)
body:
How do you like #DoctorWho season 11 with #JodieWhittaker so far? Here’s a rant about some rants… sort of, yeah.

This will be a short rant, so hold on to your seats. So… Seven episodes into season 11 of Doctor who, I stumbled upon a few – how shall I put it – “interesting” takes. For the most part, I see positive reviews, but every now and then, there are some really seething videos out there, with tons of venom… People care. Well, sort of. So what are the more negative comments so far? I guess there are 3…
